nodes.text: Ozeer Tenzer was a male mercenary sent on Twon Ketee by Regent Solculvis to stop Han Solo and his crew from hunting rathtars. He wore a set of white and red armor similar to that of the Galactic Republic's clone troopers and the Galactic Empire's stormtroopers. He usually used a pair of blaster pistols and a blaster rifle.
Ozeer Tenzer was an original character featured in LEGO Star Wars: The Force Awakens.
